survey_response.review_text: She is simply the best!!!! Very friendly and gentle handling me. I never had an experience with a dentist as good as her.
Great. She explained everything to me clearly and told me how to take care of my dental hygiene in the future

I visited Dr Tabrez for having dental implant. DR Tabrez was very friendly at the same time very professional. I had watched videos regarding the procedure and was very apprehensive but DR Tabrez first evaluated my teeth gave me the options explained the course and then the procedure itself was so pleasant. The anesthesia was vey good, he let me close my mouth every minute it was the best dental experience that i had ever had. His wife Dr ameerah is also very pleasant and together they form a really good team. I highly recommend Dr Tabrez to anyone who needs work to be done on their teeth

Doctor communcation regarding the illness and treatment was simple and sober to understand.
But for me was doctor' freindliness nature while treating the problem was win win situation for me because the day before treatment I was very much concerned about my problem.Thus leading to treatment satisfaction.

I had a severe tooth ache and after a thorough examination  Dr Ameera advised a root canal treatment for the tooth, the procedure was super smooth and I didn't feel a thing during the whole treatment.
Hands down the best dental experience, would definitely  recommend  them.

I took my 6 year old daughter for her cavities. A chocolate lover, she had 6 cavities. In a single sitting Dr Ameera was able to fill all of them. Dr Tabrez kept encouraging my daughter that you are a strong girl. The procedure went well. No tears were shed at all. She may need Route canal for one of her teeth and she is most excited to go back! Says it all. Thank you to the Team Swiss Dental Aesthetics.

I had visited Swissdentalaesthetics due to presence of unusual coffee stains and had desired removal of them. I was in an urgent need to get my teeth whitening done due to important social commitments. Dr Ameera explained me the entire process and performed a quick whitening session that lasted for only 30 minutes. I am really amazed at the results and I really appreciate the care and comfort provided by the doctor. I must say it’s a must visit place for all your dental needs.
Dr Ameera is best to treat dental issues with full confidence and minimum time. Clinic is very calm and cool . I will give 5  star for her.

True professional 
Dr Ameera n Dr Tabrez both are a boon to dental issues one really feels comfortable under the hands of these dictors
